{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act34side", "eventName": "生路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BP-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "犧牲與代價", "storyInfo": "西昆妲意外得知資料分析師的隱情，失蹤案有了新的方向。戰場形勢突變，儘管仍有顧慮，但在克萊門莎執政官的推動下，三位深海獵人加入航道計劃，正式參與作戰。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g1_beaconsquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "語音記錄#21", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "（未知語言，未知時間）", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "瓦萊莉婭已經回來半個月了，但從塔羅斯發出的包裹恐怕是到不了了。那些珍貴的技術原型和生物樣本，連帶著我訂購的那台民用級環境模擬單元，一同喪失了音訊。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "沒有播報，也沒有事故報告，宇宙毫無徵兆地對我們關上了門。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "可憐的母親，得在維生艙再熬些時日了。憑私心講，是我堅持要在模擬環境裡與她告別的。直到進入休眠的前一刻她還想著見見孫輩，我該怎麼告訴她，她想像中的孫輩根本不存在？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她一定是還活在那個樞紐鋪滿星海的輝煌年代，才會相信生命的延續不是徒增苦痛。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我為求穩妥才選了塔衛聯合工業的產品。母親太機敏，上一代的模擬技術她一定能識破。可我早該料到如今的星際運輸有多大風險。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "瓦萊莉婭的假期用完了，她回去的時候仍在喋喋不休地談著她那些宏大的使命，沒有表現出一點遺憾。我不知道她是剛剛放下，還是早就不在乎了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我早晚也會在那張同意書上簽字，關停母親的維生艙吧。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$storyendjp_intro", "key": "$storyendjp_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您怎麼來了？", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來看看你，卡西婭。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛接受過胚胎分離手術，設施管理所應該允許你暫停工作好好休息。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您知道，胚胎分離手術對身體的損害幾乎可以忽略不計，不至於需要休息那麼久。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#4$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一時分不清您是關心我，還是關心孵育室裡的那個小傢伙，阿維圖斯老師。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#4$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我自然是關心你的，但一個新生的孩子，在如今的阿戈爾也同樣值得關注。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他降生之後，你會選擇親自撫養他嗎，還是交給公共養育所？", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我傾向於不去考慮這個問題，太遙遠……太遙遠了。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#2$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來見你之前，我去了趟醫院。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫院？", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#6$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨天的那場戰鬥你肯定知道。你不會錯過任何消息，對吧？", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩支艦隊，一千多名軍團戰士，最後僅僅只有二十六人倖存。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "航道計劃已經進行到最緊要的關頭，彌利亞留姆卻在此時遭遇了遠航以來最慘重的犧牲。最近城市裡也發生了許多異常……", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿維圖斯老師，您想說什麼？", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海巡隊已經去找過你了吧，卡西婭？", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#6$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於那個失蹤的資料分析師……", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#6$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿維圖斯老師。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#2$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您知道嗎，在您整理的所有文獻裡，我最喜歡的其實是那本《生活的死亡》，儘管它談不上有什麼學術價值。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那本書的出現只是個意外。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三百多年前，四位偉大的先史文明研究者在地幔遺跡群取得重大發現，無數珍貴的技術資料被帶回了阿戈爾。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相比所有那些技術圖紙和理論著作，一份日記般的語音文件確實是不值一提。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以它靜靜地在科學院的資料庫裡躺著，是您出於好奇，將它們解譯，製作成了通俗讀物。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不過是一個普通的前人類在漫長旅程中的喃喃自語。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我很喜歡這個前人類的故事，老師。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#5$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我喜歡經由他的眼睛所見到的真實。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#5$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾將無數星球統籌為一體的體制在崩塌，曾使諸多族類連成一心的信任在瓦解。物資的匱乏，技術的失利，哲學與藝術的沉默……", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#5$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論寄託了多少憧憬與想像，那些偉業最終都悄無聲息地淪為死灰……就像信標塔裡已經死去的那些浮游機械。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#5$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡西婭，你是在感同身受他的絕望嗎？", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#6$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我之前從沒有在你身上看到過絕望的影子。你甚至選擇讓自己的孩子降生在一個隨時可能面臨毀滅的未來。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#6$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是絕望之人所能做出的選擇。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#6$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我確實完全不感到絕望。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#2$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個古板、頹唐的中年男人……我甚至無法用任何方式與他產生共鳴。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是很欣賞您藉由他過去的見聞，巧妙地撕開了如今蒙在所有阿戈爾人眼前的這塊華美的畫布。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我們必須接受曾引以為傲的事物和品質在此刻毫無作用，或許它們本來就存在瑕疵或謬誤，是這場浩劫讓它們暴露了出來。”", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "擺脫了生存的憂慮，人就會開始在意價值。我們期望自己的思想、作為，乃至存在本身都有價值。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿戈爾的全套體制，都是為發掘人的價值而設計的。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而價值是脆弱的。只需要換一個角度去解讀，偉大的就會顯得渺小，醜陋的就會顯得美麗。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜，出於某種惰性，人們大多不願脫離自己所熟悉的角度。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以人們總是仰賴一成不變的價值而活，當這些價值崩塌的時候，他們也會隨之崩潰。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，就像您現在這樣。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的絕望是從什麼時候開始滋長的？從彌利亞留姆離開本境開始，還是更早些，從您的密人離世時？", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……卡西婭？", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#6$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過還是感謝您今天來看望我。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#11$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您提醒了我，我確實還有需要完成的事，而時間已經不多了。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#7$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊門莎，你竟然允許類似的悲觀情緒在自己的城市蔓延？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "《生活的死亡》，阿維圖斯整理出版的先史日記。它在問世當年，成了最受公民們歡迎的讀物。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "窺伺一種陌生的生活，無聊而愚蠢的獵奇心態。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭，這其中的隻言片語，已經足以在陸地上的任何國家引發軒然大波。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個微小的切面，靠著字裡行間的疲憊與絕望，比任何數據都更生動地展現了一個輝煌的文明如何走上末路。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#6$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在如今的阿戈爾，它真的能算是一種“完全陌生”的生活嗎？", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#6$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿戈爾是先史文明的繼承者，但絕非其附庸。我們本不必對那些疲憊與絕望也產生認同。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿戈爾之所以屹立不倒，在於它不可被摧毀的理性。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是理性，讓人們意識到阿戈爾乃至全人類的覆滅，是一種切實存在的可能性。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連那些可憎的墮落者，他們的選擇有時也出自長久的審視與慎重的思考。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在軍團服役的日子裡，親手處決過的深海教徒不在少數。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一如你不得不親手處決那些失控的獵人。你我只是職責太重，沒有資格依賴感性。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#14$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而您依據理性所做出的決斷，就是讓剛剛返回阿戈爾的深海獵人，貿然加入航道計劃的作戰之中？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#14$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希……", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位，請看我們身後的信標塔。曾經，它是前人所構想的星際征途的重要一環。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔內孕育了數以億計的浮游機械。最先突破電子雲層的阿戈爾城市會將它們播撒在星海之間。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們將自我增殖、自我修復，串聯成長明不熄的路網。借助路網，我們的艦隊將實現星際層面的自由躍遷。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海嗣危機爆發後，阿戈爾對星空的探索陷入停滯，需要由十幾座城市共同維持的生物供能系統也被切斷。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "浮游機械不相容一般的能源形式，失去了為它們專門打造的供能系統，所有浮游機械都“死”在了塔內。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但經過技術院同僚的合力改造，如今，這座塔依然能以另一種方式為我們點亮道路。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彌利亞留姆離開本境以來，一直在持續往海嗣巢穴內投放信標，海量的數據將匯集到這座塔的中控室……", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "透過對巢穴的精準定位，第Ⅳ級武器將摧毀目標海域中的主要巢穴，驅離盤踞其間的海嗣集群……", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清出一片直通本境的澄澈水域——一條可供本境主力通行的航道。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海嗣或許會捲土重來，但至少在相當一段時間內，它們運來的養分會不斷凋腐，它們重建巢穴的努力會徒勞無果。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執政官閣下，您是在向我們同步“航道計劃”最核心的原理。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，醫生。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨天的那場戰鬥，深海獵人只來得及救下二十六人……海嗣明顯已經有所準備。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從大洋腹地到大陸架，這座城市和海嗣纏鬥了太久，海嗣對第Ⅲ級武器的適應加快了。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第三十七號巢穴的位置過於特殊，它扼住了航道的咽喉……放棄它意味著功虧一簣。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這已經是航道開啟前的最後一戰，一切可用的力量此時都應被納入計劃，深海獵人自然也不例外。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哪怕她們才剛剛回到家鄉。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#4$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿戈爾是否能保障深海獵人安全歸來？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新的戰鬥編隊正在準備，他們將與海嗣正面交戰，創造機會，讓深海獵人得以潛入巢穴，投放信標。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但您知道這只是常規的戰術布置。我確實……無法提供萬無一失的保障。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#14$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此……", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#14$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你在擔心什麼……放心。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深海獵人的安全，由深海獵人自己保障，深海獵人的風險，也由深海獵人自己把控。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然這是兩位總戰爭設計師的共同決定，我不反對，但我保留我的意見。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭……", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#3$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感性的話語不合時宜地湧上了克萊門莎的喉嚨。"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想要表達她的愧疚、她的悔恨、她的歉意。"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想要最後給歌蕾蒂婭一個擁抱，一如歡迎她回歸時那樣。"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她沒有。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……歌蕾蒂婭。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布蘭都斯顧問已經準備好你們的機體再生手術了，去做出發準備吧。", "name": "克萊門莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g4_aegirstreet_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾麗妮閣下！", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#5$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬迪。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您消失了整整一天……", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟著海巡隊調查一些事情……我進入了一趟海洋，體驗不是很好，別問了。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢，你這段時間在做什麼？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#4$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不適應是正常的。喬迪，打起精神來，這裡可是你的家鄉。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（苦笑）", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你的樣子，你已經查過布雷奧甘的資料了？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年輕的阿戈爾人點了點頭，又搖了搖頭。"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒辦法下斷言，但我多半和那位偉大的船舶設計師沒什麼關係。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那又有什麼關係？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂亞戈叔叔希望我離開格蘭法洛，離開伊比利亞，他沒告訴我該去哪裡……", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#4$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是個阿戈爾人，阿戈爾應該會有我的位置。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可一個人總需要一點確切的聯繫，哪怕只是一個名字，一本筆記，才能真正追索他的來歷。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿維圖斯先生說，即使被海嗣危機困擾了兩百多年，阿戈爾仍然還有一百多座規模和彌利亞留姆差不多的城市。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我不是布雷奧甘的後裔，那我的祖父母，在他們成為島民前，住在其中的哪一座呢？或者說，是那些已經消失的……", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#10$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們曾從事怎樣的工作，過著怎樣的生活……他們究竟是誰？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#10$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我不該在您面前說這些。您明明也才剛來到阿戈爾，卻已經能幫助海巡隊調查案件，而我……", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是個堅定的人。", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是個在這裡做不了什麼事情的伊比利亞人。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希醫生負責與這座城市的領導者接洽，深海獵人回到了她們熟悉的戰鬥當中，而我的提燈和手炮暫時派不上什麼用場。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿戈爾允許一位黎博利參觀他們的艦船與港口，但不會讓她加入軍團，同海嗣正面作戰。我確實無法理解那種形態的戰爭。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這海洋深處，我唯一能做的，只有調查城中正在發生的異常，盡可能為伊比利亞與阿戈爾的合作排除隱患。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您為什麼跟我說這些？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬迪，我的家鄉毀於一場天災，我對它已經沒有太多印象。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我隨身攜帶的經卷，便是我和家鄉僅剩的聯繫，它救下了我的性命，成為我的指引，成為我的信仰。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可直到去過審判庭的地牢，登上“愚人號”，經歷老師的犧牲……我才弄清楚信仰到底為何物，接受它的不堪，找到它的意義。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是想說……", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬迪，我沒有你想像中那麼堅定，我的困惑和迷失並不少。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是很多時候，它會變成一個又一個亟待解決的具體問題。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逮捕作祟的深海教徒，奪回被海潮侵占的燈塔，找到失落在海上的艦船，以及，幫助我們的盟友調查一位意外失蹤的資料分析師。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家鄉也好，信仰也好，無非都是你剛剛所說的“聯繫”。繼續找吧，你會找到它的，只是過程不會很快，甚至有些痛苦。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我，能嗎？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#4$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不能嗎？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你幫助伊比利亞點亮了最後的燈塔，也救起過三位深海獵人。勞倫緹娜小姐不是說過嘛，這足以得到執政官本人的表彰。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是作為阿戈爾人，還是審判庭的書記，你都能做到很多事情。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g1_beaconsquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官！", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#5$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您已經回到了城裡……看您的表情，調查並不順利，對嗎？", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧契拉小姐？", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我正準備向克萊門莎執政官彙報案情的進展，具體的情況不方便透露。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實、其實我有事找您。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#5$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上次您找我和卡西婭了解情況的時候，我就應該想起來的。只是很小很小的一件事情，或許對整個案件壓根沒什麼幫助。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我真的很在意！", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……請說。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g5_aegirstreet_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圖利婭小姐，你是留到最後的研究員。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉抱歉，能不能再給我一點時間？", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#8$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古球藻、團窗藻、石花膜、紫苔、千燈英……剩下的不多了，我很快就能清點完！", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圖利婭小姐，不用著急，我只是來例行檢查而已。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您認識我？", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，之前發展規劃所進行調職評估，我們是同一批，你可能沒有注意到我。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是準備，帶走這些海藻？", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這應該不違反什麼程序吧？", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#4$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別緊張。這棟建築的交接工作已經完成了……留下來的這些海藻植株和培育設備，你不帶走，最後也只能批量清理。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#11$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是這麼多海藻，你也沒辦法把它們全部帶走吧。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且為了靠近陸地作業，彌利亞留姆接下來會進行針對性改造，城裡也不再有培育海藻的空間和資源。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯嗯，我知道。", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#11$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能帶走多少就帶走多少……我會想辦法，不給大家添麻煩。", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#11$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可之前火山邊的那座基地都被……", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#10$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是阿戈爾最大的瀕危植物繁育基地，我看著它被海嗣吞沒。", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#3$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些原始藻類是整片海洋裡最簡單，卻也最頑強的生命。", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論明亮的淺海，還是無光的深淵，不論平滑的海床，還是斷崖的夾縫，它們都在努力地舒展身軀。", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們與海洋同歲，是這顆星球的活化石。", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是軍團的人，沒辦法直接去斬殺海嗣，這些殘留的海藻，也沒辦法幫我們解決海嗣問題。", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我不能看著它們就這麼枯萎在這裡。", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#9$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……圖利婭小姐，你很熱愛這份工作。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，您不是嗎？", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#4$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，我的小幫手把裝載模組送過來了，我就不和您聊了。", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#8$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要幫忙嗎？", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1385_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了，謝謝。", "name": "圖利婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1385_1#11$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g1_beaconsquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼時候的事情？", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生態藝術創作所搬遷的前一天。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道她到底出了什麼事，也不知道在她的眼裡，到底是不是彌利亞留姆放棄了那座火山能源站，放棄了那個繁育基地……", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我更想像不到她會因此去做什麼不好的事情……因為她自己從來沒有放棄過什麼。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圖利婭的住所確實存放著一批水培箱，但已經空置很久……", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧契拉小姐，你剛剛說的，或許並非無足輕重的小事。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，容我冒昧地問一句，你為何對圖利婭的事情格外關注？", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照我之前聽到的，你們連朋友都算不上。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她……", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她身上有我沒有的東西。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，該說的都說完了。長官，我得趕緊回去工作。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近事情越來越多，城市單元骨架的檢修量翻了好幾倍，我的墨水都不夠用了。", "name": "盧契拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小幫手。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1401_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西昆妲指揮官。", "name": "“小幫手”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "立刻向設施管理所調取彌利亞留姆的城市資料，檢索具有封閉水培條件的場所。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，聯繫艾麗妮——", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圖利婭或許還在城內留下了其他線索，請她盡快與我會合。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}